CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 31, 1958, p. A12, reads: "Young Fry - A few of the cute-as-buttons young fry who took part in the Trendettes fashion show Saturday night at Carnegie Hall. Left to right: Beverly Elaine Hunt, Kimberly Hall, Nikki Primas, Susanne Allison Hall [Gaines] and Waldra P. Campbell."
TitMainTitle: Sarah E. Gaines pointing on left, with Beverly Elaine Hunt, Kimberly "Kim" Allison Hall, Nikki Primas, Susanne Allison Gaines, Waldra P. Campbell, and boy in background, on stage at Carnegie Music Hall for Trendettes fashion show
